name: Blue Shells
description: She sells sea shells by the sea shore ... blue ones. This beautiful illustrated phone case by Cass Deller has a standout blue sea shell design that brings summer to your phone all year round.

name: Pebbles Noir
description: Find this tasteful designer phone case from Victoria Tucker, inspired by the hewn rocks of ancient cultures, perfectly illustrated in black and cream.

name: Poppies
description: Brigitte May is an artist based in the coastal village of Sawtell. Her illustrations have swept across a broad range of projects including prints for fashion labels, children's books, ceramics, branding, homeware linens, boat and car decals and more. After working with watercolor and soft pastels for close to a decade, she's recently branched into acrylics and is enjoying the shift into something more textural. With an emphasis on earthy/pretty, Brigitte's art consistently nods to the beauty of nature.

name: Sicilia
description: Vacay vibes radiate from Fenton & Fenton's "Sicilia" Sicilian scooter phone case - embodying colors, places, and culture that inspire their journey. Part of the colorful collection, the bold design transports everyday life to distant destinations, paying homage to the brand's origins, sense of adventure, and the spirit of a life less ordinary. It encapsulates the vibrant aesthetic defining Fenton & Fenton.

name: Cross Pollination
description: Experience the preservation of nature's beauty in the Cross Pollination phone case. Exquisitely crafted to capture the intricacies of petals, this phone case shields your phone with a delicate floral design. With layers of gradient colors and light-catching wrinkles, this flowery delight is sure to turn heads. Get your Cross Pollination phone case today and bring nature's beauty everywhere.

name: The Pass
description: The Pass phone case is the ultimate accessory for any phone. With its one-of-a-kind green artwork design by Blacklist Studio, it will make your device stand out from the crowd.

name: Painted Botanic
description: This unique Painted Botanic phone case is a perfect way to show off your style. Inspired by tropical islands, it features a beautiful abstract floral pattern that will add color and life to your phone.

name: Terrazzo
description: No longer hostage to just flooring, terrazzo is a trend that is here to stay and the perfect kaleidoscope pop of color. This phone case is used with patented 3D printing process to embed this design into the layers of the tough plastic polycarbonate case.

name: Sky on Light Blush
description: A twist on the checkerboard pattern with this soft sky blue and blush pink phone case - the perfect matte phone cover for your phone.

name: The Summer
description: Brigitte May painted Summer as the winter chill started to ebb and she dreamt of moving to a seaside shack. Summer embodies all the warmth and vibrance of the summer season.

name: Yeah Nah
description: It's a "Yeah, Nah" from us. This cheeky & eye-catching phone case with 70s vibes coloring is perfect for those looking for a protective case with personality.

name: Euro Summer
description: Euro Summer is a case inspired by nothing else than a Euro Summer. This classic pattern can be found around Europe featured on many buildings and vases. Not only is this pattern iconic for Europe, but it also reminds Brigitte of the beach which is where most of a European summer should be spent.

name: One of Many
description: The One of Many phone case is designed by Aboriginal designer Ryhia Dank with vibrant colors & beautiful patterns that won't fade or rub off. This case is inspired by one of many fishing spots that Ryhia would go to, visiting after the wet when the rain had stopped and all the rivers, creeks, and waterholes would be flowing. On one side of the hills, she would fish for barramundi and stay well away from the water, away from the saltwater crocodiles, and on the other side of the hills, she would swim in the crystal clear freshwater and catch black bream.

name: Blooms
description: A watercolor ditsy floral print that whispers of a Spring garden in bloom. A beautiful combination of yellow, purple, and soft blue by artist Brigitte May will make your phone case stand out.

name: The Flow
description: A beautiful neutral phone case by Cass Deller. The "Flow" design features watercolor strokes with abstract florals, line features and ancient vases. Let your imagination run wild with this beautiful phone cover for your phone.

name: Native Garden
description: Amy Gibbs Native Garden phone case offers unique protection with captivating abstract hues of native plants. Perfect for phones, this case provides a delightful experience with both artistry and dependable protection.

name: Summer Limone
description: Brighten up your day with the Summer Limone phone case! This eye-catching Kerrie Hess design showcases a juicy lemon pattern to bring a bit of sunshine to your everyday. Get ready to make a statement with this stylish and protective accessory.

name: Toucan Blue
description: Bring a little island escape to your day-to-day with Toucan Blue, a handy phone case that packs a punch of coastal-cool vibes. With a bold blue and cream white tiled pattern, this case captures the spirit of summer days without ever needing to leave home. Go on, take a tropical getaway with Toucan Blue.

name: Burn Off
description: Comprised of vibrant eccentric circles of orange, pink, and purple, this eye-catching design is for those who like their possessions to have meaning and story. This artwork is inspired by Australia during burning off when the land is dry and the embers are coming through lighting small fires. The country needs these burn-offs to regenerate.

name: Scarlet on Blush
description: Our Scarlet Red color and Blush Pink have joined forces to create this wavy checked patterned phone case design.

name: Sping Garden
description: This colorful design phone case celebrates early spring mornings, when buds begin to bloom and stems start to grow.

name: Turkish Delight
description: Lose yourself in a world of vibrant beauty and choose a Fenton & Fenton LIFE IN COLOR bold print phone case.

name: Quince
description: Essence of adventure! The Fenton & Fenton Quince phone case captures the spirit of exploration, welcoming faraway destinations into everyday life. With stunning color combinations and vibrant designs, let the Quince case take you on remarkable journeys wherever you go.

name: Peach
description: The Henryk Studio 'Peach' phone case adds an exquisite air of artistic flair to any device, with its painterly texture and soft peachy color. Made with premium materials, its gloss design offers subtle luxury and robust protection to your phone.

name: Mati Blue Evil Eye
description: Introducing the limited edition Mati Blue Evil Eye phone case, a blue evil eye pattern case that's perfect for your phone. Crafted using our patented printing process, we've seamlessly embedded this striking design into the layers of a robust polycarbonate case.

name: Fluffy
description: Protect your phone in style with the Fluffy phone case. Its pink, foamy texture gives an eye-catching, soft feel while still providing strong protection against scratches and shocks. Show off your phone with a unique design by Henryk Studio.

name: Balmy Blue
description: Balmy blue for those forever dreaming of summer, this is the right phone case for you. This hand illustrated design by Cass Deller will bring the sunnier season to your tech. We simply love the palm trees, fruit and sailboat motifs.

name: Cherry Rose
description: This Cherry Rose phone case is a beautiful addition to your device, featuring a lush cherry design illustrated by Kerrie Hess. Printed with a high gloss finish, the vibrant photographic quality won't fade or rub off, while providing excellent protection against everyday wear and tear.

name: Vintage Jean
description: Capture vintage vibes with our Vintage Jean phone case. Combining denim blue and a unique floral print, it offers your phone style and protection. Its bright blue hue brings a luxurious touch to your device, ensuring you stand out from the crowd!

name: Squiggle
description: Vacay vibes abound with Fenton & Fenton's signature Sicilia Squiggle print, drawing inspiration from lazy beach days in Scopello, Trapani. Part of the colorful collection, these bold designs pay homage to their origins, sense of adventure, and the spirit of a life less ordinary, capturing the vibrant aesthetic that defines Fenton & Fenton.

name: Ingela
description: Ingela is a multi-abstract pattern design phone case in black, tan, and beige. In collaboration with our friends at Apero, their designs are inspired by fashion, classic simplicity, and bright detailing. We use a patented 3D printing process to embed this design into the layers of the tough plastic polycarbonate case.

name: Milidimbawarr
description: Milidimbawarr means learning or teaching. This painting is of our Bardi Bardi's (older women) teaching our young Ngila's (girls) on country. There are many things our Bardi Bardi's teach us, they can range from educating about native plants and fruits to sacred women's business.

name: My Mark
description: Ryhia created this artwork because she wanted to paint something, she was doing a lot of admin and had been on her computer for so long that she felt that she needed to stop and make something, with paint, to let her mind wander. This beautiful purple and golden yellow abstract design are what came from Ryhia's spark of creativity. Looking for something multi-color? Why not check out the similar "Close Up" design phone case? We simply love this new artwork and works perfectly for those that want a colorful standout phone case for their Apple iPhone or Samsung Galaxy phone.
